Run the following commands to make the scripts executable:
chmod +x emg_configure emg

### Usage ###
Check for required python packages:

./emg_configure

Run the application:

./emg -flag [argument]
      -h  - see options.
      -s  [serial_port] - run the emg application.
      -v  [data] - visualize data from the default csv file data.
          [path_to_csv_file] - visualize data from csv file.

Example usage:
./emg_configure
./emg -s /dev/tty<name of your serial device>

